    (Freezer) Features</title>
    <sidebar xml:id="FreezerFeatures"><para>Backup, Restore, and Disaster Recovery Service (Freezer) provides integrated tools for
        backing up and restoring cloud data in multiple use cases, including disaster recovery.
        These resources include file systems, server instances, volumes, and databases.</para>
<para>Freezer is all new for the &kw-hos; Mitaka release.</para>
